snippet.textDisplay: Among all the Noble Names I love 'Al-Hakam'- The giver of perfect justice, The one who does the perfect justice. Mazlum is holding flag,striking,crying for Justice but they couldn't get it.... So Dear Mazlum! Learn this name n rely upon the one, the everlasting, all competent, all powerful.
